        <abstract> 
<p>Has reread AG’s third <hi rend="italic">Atlantic Monthly</hi> article. It is admirable, but CD cannot go as far as AG on design.</p>  
<p>Mentions other opinions and reviews of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p>  
<p>Relates some experiments on <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi> showing its extreme sensitivity; requests some observations on orchids.</p> 
        </abstract>
